title: Life's a Bitch: Tootie's March 2015 Mix
description:
...you ain't fuckin' for free. Tootie's March 2015 Mix comes on the heels of the DJ Tootie endeavor, and includes a number tracks with Tootie-exclusive editing, both old and new.

Xzibit - Best of Things
Cash Money Millionaires featuring E-40 - Baller Blockin'
Pitbull featuring Chris Brown - International Love
Partners in Kryme - Turtle Power
V.I.C. featuring Frank Ski - Wobble
Cixx vs. The Vinyl Junk - Bounce 'N Shake
Wolfgang Gartner - Bounce
deadmau5 - Some Chords
Chocolate Puma & Firebeatz - Sausage Fest
Paula Abdul - The Way That You Love Me
Kylie Minogue - All the Lovers
Lady Gaga - MANiCURE
Ginuwine - Pony
2 Live Crew - Me So Horny
Ce Ce Peniston - Finally
Pat Benatar - Love is a Battlefield
Fleetwood Mac - Little Lies
David Bowie & Mick Jagger - Dancing in the Street
Robert Palmer - Bad Case of Loving You
Deep Purple - Smoke on the Water
Papa Roach - Broken Home
3 Doors Down - Dangerous Game
Chad Kroeger featuring Josey Scott - Hero
Alice in Chains - We Die Young (Demo Version)
Charlie Clouser - Hello, Eric

All tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
